---
title: Coconut Curry with Chickpeas topped with Yogurt & served with Basmati Rice
description: Curries are one of those meals that warm your heart and your belly, and tonight’s vegetarian version is no exception. Chickpeas, onion, and bell pepper get a super savory treatment in a coconut-based curry sauce. Toss that over rice, add a dollop of yogurt and a sprinkle of cilantro, and you have yourself one soul-satisfying meal.
